description: This project aims to develop a simple online shopping application. It covers a wide range of microservices-related topics and practices, ensuring a robust, scalable, and fault-tolerant system.

description: This Repository for a Web-based Information System for SD Sitorus Godang, built on Microservices Architecture. With five independent services—schedule, subjects, announcements, syllabus, and account management—it ensures robust functionality and communication. Developed in Golang for efficiency and resilience.
